There are four seasons: spring, hot summer, fall, and cold winter. In my hometown, there are some famous grasslands, for example: Hulunbeir Grassland, Horqin Grassland, ect. In summer, you can enjoy stunning scenery on the grassland and and the local herdsmen are very enthusiastic. While during winter you will see snow, in case of long and cold winter, people are used to store lots of vegetables, like potatos and Chinese cabbages.\n' const Navigate = useNavigate() const Me = () =>{ Navigate('/') } return(
